  "texts": [
    "Therefore, these limitations pose a huge barrier to implement AI in ISAC systems with limited training samples and low latency requirements [238].To avoid model bias, effective data preprocessing, such as data cleaning, is essential before training.",
    "In addition, GAI and few-shot learning are two potential solutions to deal with the challenges of limited training samples.",
    "Leveraging the powerful generation capability, GAI can generate many new samples similar to the original ones, which is beneficial for improving the accuracy and robustness of the AI model.",
    "Few-shot learning, such as meta learning and TL, enables the AI model to learn the underlying pattern from limited training samples [276].",
    "Apart from the advantages of low training data requirement, few-shot learning can also reduce the training time and cost, thus emerging as a low-cost approach for training AI models."
  ],
